      "code": "s = raw_text\n# Find all occurrences of Arabic ornate parentheses\nsegments = []\nfor m in re.finditer(r'﴿([^﴿﴾]+)﴾', s):\n    inner = m.group(1)\n    start = m.start(1)\n    end = m.end(1)\n    segments.append((start, end, inner))\nlen(segments), segments[:10]",
